<h4 id="效果图"><a href="#效果图" class="headerlink" title="效果图"></a>效果图</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/liuminchao7/img/raw/master/Next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/1.png" alt="image-20200710205355961"></p>
<h3 id="修改网站图标"><a href="#修改网站图标" class="headerlink" title="修改网站图标"></a>修改网站图标</h3><p>Next支持修改图标</p>
<ul>
<li><p>  下载16x16以及32x32大小的PNG格式图标，放到<code>/themes/next/source/images/</code>下</p>
</li>
<li><p>打开<code>themes/next/</code>下的<code>_config.yml</code>，查找<code>favicon</code></p>
  <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">copyfavicon:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">small:</span> <span class="string">/images/cat-16x16-next.png</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">medium:</span> <span class="string">/images/cat-32x32-next.png</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">apple_touch_icon:</span> <span class="string">/images/apple-touch-icon-next.png</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">safari_pinned_tab:</span> <span class="string">/images/logo.svg</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#android_manifest: /images/manifest.json</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#ms_browserconfig: /images/browserconfig.xml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>  修改<code>small</code>和<code>medium</code>的路径为下载的图标路径</p>
<p>  我在 <a href="https://favicon.io/">favicon.io</a> 找到的   选择了红心    表示活力  朝气    以及给满屏白色填一些颜色</p>
